### Récupérer tous les workspaces (Pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/workspaces
Accept: application/json

### Créer un Workspace
POST http://localhost:8080/api/workspaces
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer "replace it by accessToken"

{
  "name": "Projet Maintenance",
  "slug": "maintenance-2026"
}

